Summary: A container that arranges its children in a horizontal or vertical flow.

FlowContainer is a container that arranges its children in a horizontal or vertical flow. It is a subclass of BoxContainer.

Inherits: BoxContainer < Container < CanvasItem < Node < Object

This class does not contain any methods or properties.
