Document: FlowContainer
Path: godot/classes/class_flowcontainer.rst
Summary: A container that arranges its child controls horizontally or vertically and wraps them around at the borders.

FlowContainer is a container that arranges its child controls horizontally or vertically and wraps them around at the borders. This is similar to how text in a book wraps around when no more words can fit on a line.
