Document: FlowContainer
Path: godot/classes/class_flowcontainer.rst
Summary: Defines properties for controlling the alignment and layout of child controls within a FlowContainer.

Properties:
* alignment (AlignmentMode): The alignment mode for the container. Default: 0.
* last_wrap_alignment (LastWrapAlignmentMode): The alignment mode for the last wrapped line. Default: 0.
* reverse_fill (bool): If true, the container will fill from right-to-left (or bottom-to-top for vertical containers). Default: false.
* vertical (bool): If true, the container will arrange its children vertically. Default: false.
